>\n", "last_modified": 1688601471, "replies": 62, "id": 954254}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 206421, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3852, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 628351, "username": "wotype", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wotype", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c5e0c6919083f4552d45b0ad8969b68d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c5e0c6919083f4552d45b0ad8969b68d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c5e0c6919083f4552d45b0ad8969b68d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1683703409, "last_modified": 1687849781}, "last_reply_by": "laydown", "last_touched": 1688610046, "title": "打算从电报转移阵地了，有什么推荐吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/954345", "created": 1688548605, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1688548605, "replies": 58, "id": 954345}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 1629, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 1557, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 615227, "username": "kuingsmile", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kuingsmile", "website": "https://www.horosama.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "Kuingsmile", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_mini.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_normal.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_large.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_xlarge.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_xlarge.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_xlarge.png?m=1684770550", "created": 1676945568, "last_modified": 1684770550}, "last_reply_by": "fredweili", "last_touched": 1688609829, "title": "家庭第一台车 无油牌 只能买混动 求推荐~", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/954243", "created": 1688529287, "deleted": 0, "content": "基本情况：南方城市，已婚，因某些原因不可能要娃，家庭目前收入去除房贷和其他各种开销后，每年净存款在 25-30W 左右（没有计算期权等暂时还不打算变现的收入），手上存款有 40W ，但明年年底交房后需要装修，预计需要 20-40W 。\r\n\r\n对车的需求：家庭第一辆车，摇了好久没有油牌，准备直接买新能源车，有过年或者节假日出去自驾玩的需求，不考虑纯电车。\r\n对车的看重主要是外观、安全性和舒适性，希望也能兼顾一点性能，由于不要小孩，对空间没有特别多的要求。\r\n日常通勤往返在 20 公里左右（新家），过年回家里程 1000 公里。\r\n\r\n预算目前还没有考虑好，初步确定在 20-40W 之间，也想听下大家的意见，以我的情况大概多少钱的车最合适，可以不会有太大的负担~\r\n\r\n请大家帮忙推荐推荐车型，写写大家~", "content_rendered": "<p>基本情况：南方城市，已婚，因某些原因不可能要娃，家庭目前收入去除房贷和其他各种开销后，每年净存款在 25-30W 左右（没有计算期权等暂时还不打算变现的收入），手上存款有 40W ，但明年年底交房后需要装修，预计需要 20-40W 。</p>\n<p>对车的需求：家庭第一辆车，摇了好久没有油牌，准备直接买新能源车，有过年或者节假日出去自驾玩的需求，不考虑纯电车。\n对车的看重主要是外观、安全性和舒适性，希望也能兼顾一点性能，由于不要小孩，对空间没有特别多的要求。\n日常通勤往返在 20 公里左右（新家），过年回家里程 1000 公里。</p>\n<p>预算目前还没有考虑好，初步确定在 20-40W 之间，也想听下大家的意见，以我的情况大概多少钱的车最合适，可以不会有太大的负担~</p>\n<p>请大家帮忙推荐推荐车型，写写大家~</p>\n", "last_modified": 1688529287, "replies": 57, "id": 954243}]